data.description: Welcome home to Traditions at Crystal Lake a highly sought after south Henry County community! EXCELLENT VALUE.  Only property for sale in the community with a FULL WALK-OUT Basement.  Practically a NEW HOME.  Don't Miss your opportunity.  Our loss is YOUR GAIN.  No detail is left behind in this beautiful single-family home featuring an exquisite brick and craftsman exterior. Spacious home on a basement features 5 bedrooms, 3 full baths, and an open layout on the main level. The stunning galley kitchen features an expansive island with high quality quartz. Upstairs you will find a spacious foyer leading to a large homeowner's suite with sitting room, dual closets, large shower with separate tub.  Enjoy a book by the fireplace or a glass a wine upstairs unwinding in your oversized master retreat. Full daylight basement is READY for you to unleash your HGTV creative skills. This community sits within 3 miles of shopping, including clothing, home decor stores, groceries, Home Depot and easy access to I-75.
